<title>fy ṭryq ạljljtẖẗ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- fy ṭryq ạljljtẖẗ qd sạr ywmaⁿạ sydy
 wạljnwd tsʿy̱ ky tkẖly ạlṭryq
 ạ̹dẖ tzạḥm ạljmyʿ lyrwạ kyf ykạfạ̉ ạlṣdyq
 2- kạn ynzf ḥbyby bsyạṭ ḍrbwh
 wbtạj ạlsẖwk rby mlkwh
 bṣrạkẖ ạlhạzỷyn wbḥkm mwt ạlʿạr krmwh
 ạlqrạr- fy ṭryq ạljljtẖẗ sạr ạ̹lhnạ ạlḥbyb
 sạr ṭwʿaⁿạ wạkẖtyạraⁿạ llṣlyb
 qbl yswʿ ạlmwt mn ạ̉jlk wmn ạ̉jly
 fy ṭryq ạljljtẖẗ sạr ạlḥbyb ạ̹ly̱ ạlṣlyb
 3- mtẖl sẖạẗ sạqwạ rby lldẖbḥ ạ̉kẖdẖwh
 whw ạlmsyạ ạldẖy ạntẓrwh
 wḥznh llgẖdr fạq ậlạm jnbh ạlmṭʿwn
 bdmh ạlkrym gẖfr llạ̉tẖym
 bṣlbh fy ạ̉wrsẖlym</lyrics>
</song>